OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnpaid state pension: 'I'm 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdisgusted by delays'       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%title3
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pensioners who have just turned 66 have
OL,6, spoken of their stress and anger after 
OL,7, failing to be paid their state pension.
OL,9,FBacklogs in processing applications at 
OL,10,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions   
OL,11,F(DWP) mean thousands of people have not
OL,12,Freceived their entitlement on time.    
OL,14,FOne told the BBC she "wanted to cry"   
OL,15,Fand "felt like she didn't count" after 
OL,16,Fher payments were not made.            
OL,18,FThe department has apologised, blaming 
OL,19,Fthe pandemic and staffing issues for   
OL,20,Fthe delays.                            
